Package: c4p-social
Version: 1.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Patrick Anderson <patrickanderson@computers4people.org>
Depends: curl, git, dos2unix
Description: C4P Fully Local Social Media Monitor
 Self-hosted social media monitoring and AI content generation system
 for Computers 4 People. Includes Docker, Ollama, PostgreSQL, Postiz,
 and a MWF email digest powered by DeepSeek R1.
